name: Cream Champagne South Sea Shell Pearl Sterling Silver Necklace
description:
JLYNN design - South Sea Shell Pearl in Cream Champagne Gold have been created in a classic, elegant style.  The South Sea Pearl Shell Teardrop (~20mm in length) is highly reflective - so will catch the light and many eyes!  They are accented with a Sterling Silver fringe bead cap, stamped 925 bail and Swarovski Crystalized Pearl.  Pendant is hand wire-wrapped with Sterling Silver findings for added security & durability.  Sterling Silver chain is a Twisted Rope style and 20" in length.  Necklace comes in a protective pouch and white sheer gift bag - suitable for gift giving. 
Measurements:
Pendant (South Sea Shell Pearl) is ~1 3/8" in length
Chain is 20" long
